room_title: Escape room "Time Machine" by Red Door Escape Room in Oklahoma City
room_description: When your Uncle tells you not to touch his time machine, you only have one thought on your mind.... Now you're scattered through time, trying to bring your team back to 2020 in one piece. With a 10% escape rate, only the bravest, the most daring and the most talkative teams survive. If it's your first or second time playing an escape room, we highly recommend playing Fair Game first.
